OL,3,CWhat is 'Super El Nino' and could it
OL,4,Cmake this summer much hotter?
OL,6,FForecasters are watching for "perhaps
OL,7,Fthe most significant El Nino this
OL,8,Fcentury".
OL,10,FBut what is El Nino and how could it
OL,11,Faffect us here in the UK? ITV News
OL,12,Fexplains.
OL,14,FWhat does El Nino actually mean?
OL,16,FEl Nino was named in the 1600s by
OL,17,FSpanish-speaking fishermen off the
OL,18,Fwest coast of South America who
OL,19,Fnoticed unusually warm waters
OL,20,Fappearing in December.
OL,26,@kD@UTwoD@[TwrD@RTwvD@PTwxD@FTw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
