PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776211372
OL,3,CWhat is 'Super El Nino' and could it
OL,4,Cmake this summer much hotter?
OL,6,FAs this happened around Christmas time
OL,7,F- it was named in reference to baby
OL,8,FJesus, or "the little boy".
OL,10,FThe opposite of this weather
OL,11,Fphenomenon is called La Nina, "the
OL,12,Flittle girl".
OL,14,FWhy are these usually warm waters
OL,15,Faround South America important?
OL,17,FAn El Nino event is an interruption in
OL,18,Fthe usual movement of weather in the
OL,19,Ftropical Pacific between South America
OL,20,Fand Australia.
OL,26,@kD@UTwsD@[TwyD@ITw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
