CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776211372
OL,3,CWhat is 'Super El Nino' and could it
OL,4,Cmake this summer much hotter?
OL,6,FAnd, because the tropical Pacific is
OL,7,Fsuch a key driver of the atmosphere, a
OL,8,Fchange in "normal" weather patterns
OL,9,Fhere impacts weather patterns around
OL,10,Fthe world with heavier rain and
OL,11,Fflooding to parts of South America for
OL,12,Fexample and, very notably, changes to
OL,13,Fmonsoons and storm tracks around the
OL,14,Fworld.
OL,16,FWhat's happening right now?
OL,26,@kD@UTw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
