PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776211372
OL,3,CWhat is 'Super El Nino' and could it
OL,4,Cmake this summer much hotter?
OL,6,FWe've been under the influence of La
OL,7,FNina since late 2024, which has
OL,8,Fslightly taken the edge off global
OL,9,Ftemperatures but now experts are
OL,10,Fseeing strong signals of a potential
OL,11,FEl Nino developing later this year -
OL,12,Fand this one is giving all the signs
OL,13,Fthat it could become a very strong
OL,14,Fevent - with the knock on effect of
OL,15,Fbigger global weather impacts.
OL,17,FHow could this affect the UK weather?
OL,19,FThere's often a lag between El Nino
OL,20,Fdeveloping, and the impacts to the UK.
OL,26,@kD@UTwoD@CTwsD@FTw{D@bTw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
