OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776211372
OL,3,CWhat is 'Super El Nino' and could it
OL,4,Cmake this summer much hotter?
OL,6,FIf it did develop during summer, which
OL,7,Fis very possible, we could have a
OL,8,Fgreater chance of higher temperatures
OL,9,Fat the end of summer.
OL,11,FA more likely outcome is that we would
OL,12,Fsee effects during the winter, as the
OL,13,Fchances of a colder winter increase.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,20,FCould this mean more global heat?
OL,26,@kD@UTw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
