FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776211372
OL,3,CWhat is 'Super El Nino' and could it
OL,4,Cmake this summer much hotter?
OL,6,FSo, while El Nino is a natural part of
OL,7,FEarth's climate system, it remains an
OL,8,Fincredibly powerful driver of global
OL,9,Fweather.
OL,11,FAs we move through this year, a strong
OL,12,FEl Nino is increasingly likely - and
OL,13,Fwhile it won't determine our day-to-
OL,14,Fday weather, it can quietly load the
OL,15,Fdice, raising the likelihood of
OL,16,Fcertain - potentially impactful -
OL,17,Fweather events both here in the UK and
OL,18,Facross the world.
OL,26,@kD@UTwnD@PTwtD@FTw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
